Once you have discovered all the IPs (external or internal) you want to scan in depth, different actions can be performed.

Nmap (Network Mapper)

    Basic Ping Scan:

           nmap -sn target.com

SYN Scan:

nmap -sS target.com

Full TCP Scan:

nmap -sT target.com

Service Version Detection:

nmap -sV target.com

Operating System Detection:

nmap -O target.com

Aggressive Scan:

nmap -A target.com

Scan Specific Ports:

nmap -p 22,80,443 target.com

Scan All Ports:

nmap -p- target.com

Script Scanning:

nmap --script vuln target.com
